So the new head of the FBI, Mueller, is telling us to steel ourselves and get used to having suicide attacks as a part of life in the U.S. in the future, just like in Israel.   Hmmm, how about no?<P>How about we give the Palestinians a home, thus removing the slightest justification for muslim suicide bombs, and then make a clear statement to all Arabs, similar to the rules in our country holding parents accountable for the actions of their children, or dog owners accountable for the actions of their dogs.<P>If you are responsible for rearing and sheltering an entity that goes out and harms others, you will pay the price on their behalf.  Meaning, the next time a terrorist hits America, there will be no 'steeling' ourselves to it no.  There will be severe retribution.  It will take the form of a firm demand for every change we will feel necessary in order for that country to avoid ever generating a general suicide bomber mentality again, or if that is rejected, a retribution upon the entirety of the people who generated this lunacy, as a punishment to them for not doing a better job of policing the way they raise themselves.<P>If a man raises a savage pitbull that kills my brother, that man will pay the ultimate price for this, even though he did not in fact do the killing.<P>Similarly, if a country cultivates a fanaticism that generates people who kill my fellow Americans by the cowardly use of suicide bombs, that country will have to pay the ultimate price for this, even though it did not in fact do the killing.<P>Simple logic really.  Anything less, including any of this "steeling ourselves" to suicide bombing as a part of life, is simply put, unacceptable, and fuck Mueller for even suggesting it.<P>--------------------<P>Scaled, for her pleasure<BR><A HREF="http://drow.org/eq/roster/viewprofile.php?name=Sssorn" TARGET=_blank>Profile</A> | <A HREF="http://www.drow.org/news.shtml" TARGET=_blank>BotS</A>
